Who is my Representative?

Figures listed on this page reflect federal career totals from all pro-Israel PACs:

  • Donations: Direct and conduit contributions to campaign accounts

  • Expenditures: Independent Expenditures (ad spending) by Israel lobby groups

    • AIPAC: American Israel Public Affairs Committee

    • AGG: Americans for Good Government

    • AMP: American Principles

    • AUSD: Americans United in Support of Democracy

    • DMFI: Democratic Majority for Israel

    • GCSC: Grand Canyon State Caucus

    • JAC: Joint Action Committee for Political Affairs PAC

    • LFAS: Louisianans for American Security PAC

    • MDACC: Maryland Association for Concerned Citizens PAC

    • NORPAC: formerly known as North Jersey PAC

    • PIA: Pro-Israel America PAC

    • RJC: Republican Jewish Coalition

    • TPOH: To Protect Our Heritage PAC

    • USI: U.S. Israel PAC
